net.proteusframework.core.locale

Class LocalizedObjectKeyEditor

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.beans.PropertyEditorSupport
      • net.proteusframework.core.locale.LocalizedObjectKeyEditor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.beans.PropertyEditor

    public class LocalizedObjectKeyEditor
extends java.beans.PropertyEditorSupport
    Editor for LocalizedObjectKey. If the text value is a number the key will be a Long representation of the value. Otherwise the text value is assumed to be the symbolic name of a LocalizedObjectKey. Therefore, "abc" becomes LocalizedObjectKey.fromStatic("abc").
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
